e":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T02:56:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a8164181a2b87bf793f701ce2f4b4d3e0e1241d","tid":2217848,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T03:08:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24d83257ba77069eadd084ef9bbaf4aa2dd2142b","tid":2217848,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:30:09.000Z","msg":"俾人踩到上心口喇！<br />\n十四億人一齊衝啦"},{"pid":"429fb4655bac97a707fe93b652e42923a6f5f8fe","tid":2217848,"uid":4575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:37:19.000Z","msg":"講自衛邊夠中國黎，日日打飛機打上天"},{"pid":"b06da58cded4c6434c2ee777ac47c02f17bb8001","tid":2217848,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T13:12:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">印度軍隊獲得授權！「解放軍若接近就開火」</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n2020/09/26 18:50<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中、印邊境衝突，造成兩國局勢緊張。<span class=\"red\">印度一名軍官透露，現在在邊境的印度軍隊已經獲得授權，只要解放軍接近、危及安全，就可開槍自衛。</span><br />\n<br />\n印度多間媒體引用一名不透露姓名的印軍高級官員在一次聯訪時的內容。他指出，中國想要以人數優勢壓制印軍的策略不會得逞，先前6月15日發生的衝突加拉萬河谷近戰衝突可能不會再發生，「現在，如果你們靠近，我們將開火」。至於接近到何種程度會開火？軍官指出，將視白天、黑夜等不同情形條件而定。<br />\n<br />\n中國與印度本週舉行會談裝，雙方同意不再向前線增派部隊，該軍官指出「這是好的開始」，不過他也說，除非等到有具體行動，否則印度不會降低警戒，「我們的立場是中國先行動（撤軍），再換我們移動，這是一個建立信任的良好開始」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3304113\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3304113&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzrCEdHrHTgyyxjjYSTVVVd4%3D&h=9a38742b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3304113&h=c014139f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3304113</a>"}]}